### 8. TERMINATION

#### 8.1 By You
You may terminate this Agreement at any time by uninstalling the Software and ceasing use. If you have purchased a Commercial License, Licensor may offer a refund under its refund policy (see [lxveace.com/refunds](https://lxveace.com/refunds)).

